        <h2>Documentation and Support</h2>
        <p>Welcome to the Budget Claims System help page. Here you'll find detailed documentation and support for using the system.</p>
        
        <h3>Features</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#add-claim">Add Claims</a></li>
            <li><a href="#edit-claim">Edit Claims</a></li>
            <li><a href="#search-claims">Search Claims</a></li>
            <li><a href="#export-claims">Export Claims</a></li>
